data.description: If you're looking for your own private oasis, this may be the home for you! Nestled on 2.24 acres, this beautiful log cabin has lots of character, and includes 2 outbuildings, shed, and in ground heated swimming pool with pool house. This home has 3 bedrooms, 2 full baths, updated kitchen with newer appliances, new water heater, well pump, and sump pump, woodburning fireplace on the main level, and a fireplace with gas log in the basement.  The attached garage has a finished space above that would be perfect for a "man cave" or craft room/studio space.  This home is "generator ready", and also includes gas powered mantle lights throughout the home. The small, stocked pond is also a wonderful feature for a little fishing and relaxing. Sellers are giving a $20,000 credit at closing.  Ask listing agent for details. This property is a MUST SEE!
